name: Playing With Light
description:
Fireworks photographed by Fivos Doganis (@fdoganis) in Nîmes, France, in August 2021.

Celebrating the diversity and the creativity of the artists behind the first 200000 pieces of hicetnunc.

The long exposure and camera movement create a group of silhouettes of bright people of many different shapes, sizes and colors, playing with light, each in their own style.
